title: Lightning Launcher v12.7b2 [Android]
description:
Updated: 17 September 2015


For Android: 2.2 and up


WHAT'S NEW:

New feature: floating desktop! Use one of your desktops as a screen that can be displayed anywhere, anytime. Just swipe from an edge of your screen and your desktop will be displayed above any other app, always ready to launch app or display widgets, just when you need it.


For more info about this app:

 
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=net.pierrox.lightning_launcher_extreme
